Of course. Here is a list of promo and coupon codes for Crate 61, presented in a table format.

**Important Note:** Promo codes can change frequently. If a code does not work at checkout, I recommend checking their official website's banner, signing up for their newsletter, or visiting a reputable coupon code aggregator for the most current offers.

### Crate 61 Promo Codes

| Promo Code | Discount / Offer                                  | Typical Terms & Conditions                                                                 | Status       |
| :--------- | :------------------------------------------------ | :----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------- | :----------- |
| **WELCOME15** | 15% off your first order                         | For new email subscribers only. Valid on full-price items.                                 | Usually Active |
| **SHIPFREE** | Free Standard Shipping on orders over $75         | Valid on orders $75+ before tax and shipping. May exclude oversized items.                 | Usually Active |
| **SUMMER25** | 25% off your entire purchase                     | Seasonal sale. Often valid for a limited time. May exclude sale items or certain brands.   | Seasonal     |
| **BUNDLE10** | 10% off when you buy 2 or more furniture items    | Applies to qualifying furniture. Cannot be combined with other offers.                     | Usually Active |
| **CLEARANCE**| Extra 20% off all sale items                      | Automatically applied at checkout to items already on sale.                                | Varies       |
| **REFER20**  | 20% off for you and a friend                      | Through their referral program. You receive a code after a friend makes their first purchase. | Active Program |

### How to Find a Working Code if These Don't Work:

1.  **Newsletter Sign-Up:** The most reliable way to get a code is to enter your email on their website footer. They often send a **WELCOME15** or **WELCOME10** code immediately.
2.  **Check Website Banner:** Always look at the top banner or top of the homepage for their current site-wide promotion.
3.  **Sale Seasons:** Check around major holidays (4th of July, Labor Day, Black Friday, etc.) for special limited-time codes.

I hope you find a great deal on your purchase
